{"tid":291916,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"漁民屠殺領航鯨 法羅群島變血色海洋","createTime":"2017-06-21T02:56:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T10:24:26.000Z","uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4b9c60a31afc9c077a035b9946086cf27b0e17f1","tid":291916,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T02:56:39.000Z","msg":"位於挪威海和北大西洋之間海域的法羅群島（Faroe Islands），每年都會舉行夏季獵鯨活動，數以百計領航鯨被迫游到岸邊遭人逐一殺害，血水將大海染成一片鮮紅色。<br />\n<br />\n漁民駕駛漁船和快艇將領航鯨趕至海灘，靜候灘上的居民一湧而上，有人甚至穿上全副潛水裝參與活動。他們用繩索將鯨魚拖近岸邊，然後用利刀和魚叉把牠們殺死。<br />\n<br />\n領航鯨每年夏季會經過法羅群島海域，當地居民早在幾百年前已開始每年獵鯨，取肉為食，鯨脂亦可製成潤滑油等，這個傳統保留至今，但多次惹來國際批評。<br />\n目前全球估計有100萬條長鰭領航鯨，以及約20萬條短鰭領航鯨。<br />\n英國《每日郵報》/《蘋果》資料室  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170620/large/1497949516_eb28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170620%2Flarge%2F1497949516_eb28.jpg&h=3c735cda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170620/large/1497949422_eb19.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170620%2Flarge%2F1497949422_eb19.jpg&h=cc77f424&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edbc13cd63111aef0d779dea47c5adf8823f08c6","tid":291916,"uid":98692,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T02:57:37.000Z","msg":"虛偽，你食魚生唔可憐下條魚？"},{"pid":"eae3defc9d635ab0159e2a955a16a92313f84620","tid":291916,"uid":55023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T03:15:22.000Z","msg":"好撚恐怖"},{"pid":"fe1a3fafa3644febfa941140c215329bee4ba586","tid":291916,"uid":89757,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T03:21:06.000Z","msg":"如果係殺黎食同賣就冇咩問題<br />\n但好似海豚灣咁就仆街啲"},{"pid":"8e0797623c2c5553c41ed8160d6dcbe0354570b5","tid":291916,"uid":79471,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T03:22:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>虛偽，你食魚生唔可憐下條魚？</blockquote><br />\n真 濫捕得好誇張 班日本仔痴撚線<br />\n個海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe32c7dcac7169367256d2840fb9e67009934e23","tid":291916,"uid":57460,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T03:31:13.000Z","msg":"仆街嘅係人類濫捕，然後另一邊又話要平衡生態。<br />\n<br />\n都係嗰句啦，正常食物鏈攝食係冇問題，<br />\n但持續濫捕破壞就只會最後人類要找數。"},{"pid":"307d4b8f51d6fd9d0323f4da188b6ce2adb4527a","tid":291916,"uid":42586,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T05:14:49.000Z","msg":"一年先百零條有撚所謂咩<br />\n<br />\n好過日本個度借科學研究為名殺啲瀕臨絕種鯨魚吖"},{"pid":"3779d2d95413673bc1fbddfb024923bf304c4bfd","tid":291916,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:26:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仆街嘅係人類濫捕，然後另一邊又話要平衡生態。<br />\n<br />\n都係嗰句啦，正常食物鏈攝食係冇問題，<br />\n但持續濫捕破壞就只會最後人類要找數。</blockquote><br />\n最後啲魚絕晒種<br />\n人類無魚食了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c9b400cfd4246211494476232e73b703d48314c","tid":291916,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:55:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fadeac6f318faa03de638e020dd97b72fcea4579","tid":291916,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:57:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一年先百零條有撚所謂咩<br />\n<br />\n好過日本個度借科學研究為名殺啲瀕臨絕種鯨魚吖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果 要進行科學研究 而殺生, 我覺得無問題<br />\n<br />\n好多白老鼠 都係因為做實驗而死左<br />\n唔通你又叫科學家 唔可以再用白老鼠做實驗??<br />\n<br />\n死一百隻白老鼠, 可以令科學家研究到一隻新藥, 救番幾千萬人"},{"pid":"3f75338cf35fdfc2e352364dd91389b344127bbc","tid":291916,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:57:40.000Z","msg":"人類用左幾十萬年爬上食物鍵頂端然後同你和理非？on9"},{"pid":"4f70b309ee66a7eaaf14c6aff6876172c33f054b","tid":291916,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T15:58:08.000Z","msg":"人類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514233cb3af9a5e1e0e3eb3968b7251d5eff64eb","tid":291916,"uid":82929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:15:18.000Z","msg":"領航鯨會係群島附近捉魚。唔控制佢地數量，班島民會捉少左魚，所以一年要屠一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 順便嚇走其他死剩種<br />\n佢地祖先教落既生存之道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上個群島接近北極圈，唔夠日照出產農作物，島民要用盡一切方法保持魚獲量，唔係就乞食餓死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有人會話搞生態旅遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但咁撚北，水溫咁凍，個海唔會有珊瑚礁<br />\n出到公海又要同歐聯漁船/加拿大漁船/美國漁船競爭魚獲<br />\n<br />\n為左保持沿岸魚獲量，一年屠一次都唔過份<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鳩估島民屠鯨既藉口/傳統"},{"pid":"94595210f36b3b81c4c5195c478f456b78e263b3","tid":291916,"uid":87613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:18:53.000Z","msg":"外國有個on9組織PETA,鬼佬殺鯨魚就得,中國狗肉節屌哂成個亞洲係野蠻人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775bd7d7c129ddac77a53d377567a98da388cc23","tid":291916,"uid":6132,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T17:01:39.000Z","msg":"On9新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一年得一次，殺得百幾條都好嘈，中國人食魚翅一日都唔知幾多條鯊魚啦<br />\n啲人永遠係待人以嚴，律己以寬<br />\n人地殺鯨班人先無啦啦萌生憐憫之心<br />\n平時食雞牛豬又唔見你憐憫下佢地？"},{"pid":"74a516bf2a4ae18f8c4a6da640cb69581feb6808","tid":291916,"uid":83308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T23:12:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>虛偽，你食魚生唔可憐下條魚？</blockquote><br />\n真 濫捕得好誇張 班日本仔痴撚線<br />\n個海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n驗眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有閱讀障礙。請早日求醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真正盲燃。咁撚急出黎賊"},{"pid":"3343996227482e72c78a013e14a45f815b30fac1","tid":291916,"uid":56401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T23:13:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>虛偽，你食魚生唔可憐下條魚？</blockquote><br />\n真 濫捕得好誇張 班日本仔痴撚線<br />\n個海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n驗眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有閱讀障礙。請早日求醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n真正盲燃。咁撚急出黎賊</blockquote><br />\n字都打唔好叫人盲撚"},{"pid":"b688c0e1b837d96272e9f6b5f04d3bc79a3e7d54","tid":291916,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T23:20:37.000Z","msg":"一車車...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ab086e8eb99eb89cce07e43f3a640333e701184","tid":291916,"uid":62815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T23:30:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一年先百零條有撚所謂咩<br />\n<br />\n好過日本個度借科學研究為名殺啲瀕臨絕種鯨魚吖</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果 要進行科學研究 而殺生, 我覺得無問題<br />\n<br />\n好多白老鼠 都係因為做實驗而死左<br />\n唔通你又叫科學家 唔可以再用白老鼠做實驗??<br />\n<br />\n死一百隻白老鼠, 可以令科學家研究到一隻新藥, 救番幾千萬人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以人類都係地球毒瘤<br />\n真正環保撚愛地球唔應該細眉細眼嘢<br />\n應該諗方法幫人口減半<br />\n地球先有得休養生息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20ea21c67eef9b250f3ebefa0b63abb0c630a564","tid":291916,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T23:40:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>虛偽，你食魚生唔可憐下條魚？</blockquote><br />\n真 濫捕得好誇張 班日本仔痴撚線<br />\n個海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n驗眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有閱讀障礙。請早日求醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clo